actual_result: Navigated to https://oda.no/, accepted cookies, searched for 'banana', and clicked the 'Legg til i handlekurven' button for 'Bananer'. The page updated to show 'Du har 1 vare i handlekurven' and a total of kr 25,20, indicating that Bananer was successfully added to the cart.
notes: The 'Legg til i handlekurven' button for Bananer was at index 14 in the previous step, but after clicking, the element at index 14 became the quantity input field with value 1, and a 'Fjern fra handlekurven' button appeared at index 13, confirming the item was added.
